N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 4.1 - Fee for the procurement opportunities newsletter

State Regulations

Except as otherwise provided in section
4.2, an annual fee of $125 shall be
charged for the New York State Contract Reporter, the procurement opportunities
newsletter published by the Department of Economic
